  "recommendations": [
    "Thomas Daurio\n\nI have had the pleasure to work with Lori Sieler while she was employed at Raven Industries as a program manager.  Lori was a key member in Siemen's PCA outsourcing project.  Siemens was able to move the products in record time without affecting on time deliveries and clearing existing backlog.  This was accomplished by her persistence to make sure milestones were met and her constant attention to detail.  Lori always looked for ways that were beneficial to both her company and the customer.  This approach to partnership and project management was the model that Siemens and Raven Industry used as a benchmark which other projects were evaluated.I wish all my supplier project managers were like Lori.  I highly recommend her for any organization.   Lori is a high impact performer that will make an immediate impact to any project or company she represents."
  ],
